  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We intend to study the cost of treatment, efficacy and adverse effects for Otitis media with
      effusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Treatment groups would be:

        1. Cefpodoxime + oxymetaxoline drops + levocetirizine

        2. Fluticasone intranasal spray

        3. Short term oral steroids

        4. Wait and watch
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
